Various demos and tools for EAD validation and processing:

ead-tidy.xsl: XSLT 2.0 Stylesheet to perform various "tidying" procedures on EAD instances 

ead_4_rules_testing.xml: sample EAD for use in testing ead_rules-iso.sch and ead_rules.sch

ead-revision:

* ead_minimal_strawman.rng: An experimental RelaxNG schema for a minimal version of EAD optimized for data interchange

* ead_revised.rng: Revised version of EAD 2002 RNG schema to test proposed changes to EAD for its upcoming release in 2013

* ead_revised_test_instance.xml: sample EAD for use in testing ead_revised.rng

* ead_revision_test_instance.xml: sample EAD for use in testing ead_minimal_strawman.rng

ead_rules-iso.sch: ISO Schematron schema to demonstrate rules checking of EAD instances 

ead_rules.sch: Schematron 1.5 schema to demonstrate rules checking of EAD instances

extend-with-nvdl: demonstration of use of NVDL to extend EAD by allowing elements from external namespaces

stripns.xsl: XSLT 2.0 stylesheet for converting EAD 2002 RNG-valid or XSD-valid instance to HTML using the eadcbs8.xsl stylesheet [must rename!]